{"tid":2317303,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警署警長涉販毒 案件轉介高等法院審理","createTime":"2020-12-08T12:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T15:17:07.000Z","uid":56115,"like":96,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"568dc4b6e612d1dd022d8c4e045240191ac6e9a8","tid":2317303,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T12:37:24.000Z","msg":"警方今年5月破獲涉及警務人員的販運冰毒案，涉案毒品重量高達<span class=\"red\">24.5公斤</span>，包括一名警署警長在內的兩男一女被控販毒罪，案件今於九龍城裁判法院再訊。控方今申請將三名被告分開兩案處理，涉案警署警長與女被告被控串謀販毒等罪，另一男被告則被控販毒罪。裁判官將兩案押後至明年1月18日在東區法院提訊，以待轉介高等法院審理。被告沒有保釋申請，繼續還柙。<br />\n<br />\n被告警署警長許思漢（41歲）原本被控於今年5月7日在帝苑酒店1517室及大坑東道111號南山邨一個單位內非法販運危險藥物。修改後的控罪則指許思漢與女被告王若男（28歲）於今年4月27日至5月7日間，在香港一同串謀販運危險藥物。惟控罪書上未有寫明毒品份量。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4455927/org/9159eee89da94ceca7d693e0598a2631.png/3MysT9cgv9cjOaHfeF8VStv65oFpXXOVqxfB-asXwfk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4455927%2Forg%2F9159eee89da94ceca7d693e0598a2631.png%2F3MysT9cgv9cjOaHfeF8VStv65oFpXXOVqxfB-asXwfk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=2ee58350&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56c06f64332f4d525e630ecb919b111486cb4519","tid":2317303,"uid":56115,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T12:37:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201208/DMP2ENWTQ5GT7K5GTPNBDZECIU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201208%2FDMP2ENWTQ5GT7K5GTPNBDZECIU%2F&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3WxURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=7f4f0709\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201208%2FDMP2ENWTQ5GT7K5GTPNBDZECIU%2F&h=714e7cd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201208/DMP2ENWTQ5GT7K5GTPNBDZECIU/</a>"},{"pid":"ce739b26759c5aa97fba2cadcb558e0b384986a3","tid":2317303,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T12:40:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" clas